sprint_goal: Establish the foundational tenant registration, user login, and role-based routing. Ensure baseline security and accessibility standards are set.
Build the complete user invitation and onboarding workflow, including security features like password reset and lockout.
Implement the core subordinate attendance workflow, including check-in/out with GPS and basic offline support.
Establish the complete team management functionality for Admins, including creation, editing, member management, and hierarchy validation.
